<section sectnbr = "9I">
<servcat sctnbr = "09" scnbr = "09">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "1">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B9901001" svcinfotypenbr = "03" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" supplyoff = "1" modify = "1">
<title>
Sun Roof System Description
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Sun roof system consists of sun roof unit, sun roof motor with sun roof control module and sun roof switch. It can perform slide and tilt operations.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sun roof system is controlled by the sun roof control module built in the sun roof motor.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sun roof switch has “SLIDE OPEN” and “TILT UP” position. By operating this switch, the sun roof performs the actions shown in the following table depending on its position.
</ptxt>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<title>
Sun roof operation table
</title>
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Sun roof switch position
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry namest = "2" nameend = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Slide operation
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Fully closed
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry namest = "5" nameend = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Tilt operation
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Fully opened
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Partially opened
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Partially opened
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Fully opened
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
SLIDE OPEN
</emph>
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
No motion
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Slide-open
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Slide-open
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Tilt-down
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Tilt-down
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
TILT UP
</emph>
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Slide-close
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Slide-close
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
