</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sun roof system has auto slide and auto tilt functions to fully open and fully close the sun roof by one switch operation.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sun roof system has anti-pinching function.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B9901001001">
<title>
Auto Slide and Auto Tilt Functions
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
For auto slide and auto tilt functions, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B9901002">Description of Auto Slide and Auto Tilt Functions</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B9901001002">
<title>
Anti-Pinching Function
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
For anti-pinching function, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B9901003">Description of Anti-Pinching Function</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
